### AppManifest API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!

### 登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 获取 CSRF
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###

### 创建应用清单
# @name createManifest
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app-manifests
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appKey": "productized_app_2026",
  "name": "产品化应用示例",
  "description": "用于产品化重构联调",
  "category": "Demo",
  "icon": "appstore",
  "dataSourceId": 1
}

###
@manifestId = {{createManifest.response.body.$.data.Id}}

### 查询清单列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app-manifests?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 查询清单详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app-manifests/{{manifestId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 发布应用（创建 release）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app-manifests/{{manifestId}}/releases
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "releaseNote": "Sprint4 first release"
}

### 工作台概览
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app-manifests/{{manifestId}}/workspace/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [兼容窗口检查] v1 接口应可继续访问（Deprecated 提示由响应头或网关提示返回）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app-manifests?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&keyword=productized
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [迁移契约占位] v2 目标路径（未落地前可能返回 404/501）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/application-catalogs?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
